THANK YOU FOR PARTICIPATING IN PROJECT KARMA

Your feedback is helping to shape the future of cannabis in Canada. Creating a Profile on Project Karma allows you to track and catalogue strains and skus as you sample them. The platform is a place to log tasting notes on new strains and SKUS and to let us know how they stack up against other products on the market With the Journal feature you can recall your experiences from past sessions and also search our database of experiences posted by other budtenders and industry insiders like yourself. From time to time, Project Karma participants are invited to weigh in on unreleased and exclusive strains before they head to market. Put that in your pipe and smoke it! There are no charges, hooks or gimmicks to participate in Project Karma. Just high vibes.

); } export default GuestDashboard;
